<h1>Normalisation Demo</h1>
<p>This page demonstrates the automatic normalisation of a chord chart.
The input below is "badly" spelled (e.g. using A# in F major) and has inconsistent spacing.
The output is generated by <code>grigson</code> in your browser.</p>

<h2>Input</h2>
<pre>---
title: Demo Song
key: F
---
| F | A# | F | C7 |
|F|Bb|C|F|</pre>

<h2>Output</h2>
<grigson-chart normalise>
  <template>---
title: Demo Song
key: F
---
| F | A# | F | C7 |
|F|Bb|C|F|</template>
</grigson-chart>
